Resume Cover Letter Winner

This project includes a career resume writing skill derived from and inspired by:

- Project: yscho03/writing-career-resume-skill
- URL: https://github.com/yscho03/writing-career-resume-skill
- Original author: 조연섭
- Blog: https://yscho03.tistory.com
- License: MIT

The original project describes a Claude Skill for generating Korean technical
career statements and resumes in Markdown. This repository adapts that idea for
an open-source workflow that combines Excel/Google Sheets career source data,
job posting analysis, resume matching, Markdown output, HTML preview, and PDF
export.

Changes in this repository include:

- Codex-compatible skill metadata and structure
- Excel/Google Sheets source-data schema
- Job posting analysis and matching-report workflow
- AI follow-up question workflow
- Resume and cover letter template selection metadata
- Markdown-to-HTML-to-PDF system design

